[[Category:Templates]]

{{Documentation subpage}}
This template creates a single succession box center column to be used with [[Template:S-start/doc|succession boxes]] for the function of listing titular titles (claimed titles with no associated authority).

==Usage==

The format is <code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>s-tul|title=''enter title here''|years=''enter years title was held here''|''parameter=''}}</code>, where ''parameter='' can be used optionally for any of the additional parameters listed in the following table. 

All succession boxes using this template should have the header ''[[Template:s-pre]]''.

:''line'' &mdash; This parameter allows an editor to designate a claimant line (such as [[Legitimist]]) beneath the title line. 
:''reason'' &mdash; Use this to provide a brief description of the reasons behind the titular title.  Be sure to wikilink and events.

This template allows for multiple row-spans using the parameter |rows=| between the template name and the first parameter.

==Example==
From the [[:en:Alfonso XIII of Spain|Alfonso XIII of Spain]] article:
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" style="font-size:95%; width:95%; overflow:auto;">
{{s-start}}
{{s-pre}}
{{s-bef|before=[[:en:Alfonso Carlos of Bourbon, Duke of San Jaime|Alphonse II]]}}
{{s-tul|title=[[:en:List of French monarchs|King of France]] and [[:en:List of Navarrese monarchs|Navarre]]
|line=[[Legitimists|Legitimist claimant]]
|years=29 September 1936 – 29 February 1941
|reason=[[July Revolution|Bourbon monarchy deposed in 1830]]}}
{{s-aft|after=[[Infante Jaime, Duke of Segovia|Jacques II]]}}
{{s-end}}
</syntaxhighlight>
